Package: istatR
Title: R Interface to the Italian National Institute of Statistics (ISTAT) API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Juan", "", , email = "juan@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides an R interface to the ISTAT SDMX RESTful API. Allows users
    to discover available datasets, explore their structure and dimensions,
    and retrieve statistical data from the Italian National Institute of
    Statistics. Based on the Python 'istatapi' package by Jacopo Attolini.
